llah is one. Among you are those with brown skin, white\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35169,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/02\/07\/quran-or-singing\/","url_meta":{"origin":35593,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Qira\u2019ah: Allah attentively listens to recitation of Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 7, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Fadalah ibn \u2018Ubayd reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah listens more intently to a man reciting the Quran aloud in a beautiful voice than an employer of singers listens to his singers.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 1340 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ibn\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":29360,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/13\/necessity-reciting-pleasant-voice\/","url_meta":{"origin":35593,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Necessity of reciting in a pleasant voice","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 13, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Lubabah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cHe is not one of us who does not recite the Quran in a pleasant voice.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 1471 Grade: Jayyid (very good) according to Al-Nawawi \u0639\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u0644\u0628\u0627\u0628\u0629 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627